# StudentHub

StudentHub is a web-based student registration and management system built using Node.js. It enables students to register, submit details, and securely store data in a database. The platform provides an intuitive interface for managing student records and streamlining the enrollment process.

## Technologies Used
- Node.js
- Express.js
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## Features
- Student Registration
- Secure Data Storage
- Student Record Management
- User-Friendly Interface

